text: int main ( void ) { int t , a , b , i , g , l , k ; scanf ( "%d" , & t ) ; for ( k = 0 ; k < t ; k ++ ) { scanf ( "%d%d" , & a , & b ) ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= a && i <= b ; i ++ ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) g = i ; } l = ( a * b ) / g ; printf ( "%d %d\n" , g , l ) ; } return 0 ; }
